Fabricated with dead-stock fabric, a reclaimed material sourced from local textile merchants. Dead-stock is often surplus cloth that has been rejected by fashion brands, due to overestimations within production and sales.

The Shirt dress is designed and produced in London, handmade by the designer in her studio in Haggerston, East London.

Any imperfections are intended in the artistic nature of the garment’s design, and shouldn’t be considered a defect or cause of complaint.
